articles.title: Fishermen protest after Pacific volcano eruption causes oil spill in Peru - CBC.ca
articles.description: An oil spill off the Peruvian coast, caused by the waves from an eruption of an undersea volcano in the South Pacific nation of Tonga, prompted dozens of fishermen to protest Tuesday outside the South American country's main oil refinery.
